      <h1>Hand the agent the keys.<em>Without actually handing it the keys.</em></h1>
      <p class="lede">A local broker that holds your secrets in one encrypted vault on your machine and hands them to apps and coding agents at the moment they need them &mdash; only inside the project boundary you bound, only for the time window you allowed, and never as a value the agent can see.</p>
